summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5746 for the improvement of A portion of The Alley in Block 10, Green Lake Reservoir Addition, being that part of the alley between 15th Avenue Northeast and 16th Avenue Northeast, from East 80th Street to Bothell Way; and certain other alleys; by paving and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 75811, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
